,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:34:38.000Z","msg":"170萬+無數未入維園既人+10多名身穿黑衣, 散場後回到警總, 追求獨立調查委員會既警員."},{"pid":"7b66c8e940d5c33c8b406648a5b773d9703869e9","tid":1485691,"uid":201385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c427bdebe19d780446fb3becd8f751fb4b66f2a1","tid":1485691,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:38:00.000Z","msg":"金鐘果邊已經散到連蘋果直播都停埋，<br />\n而政府都唔駛等人set乜鳩deadline，<br />\n宜家佢擺明好似6.9咁，同晚即刻覆左你:<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/b0JfOnr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb0JfOnr.png&h=91ad2228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69168499_10157965156552448_4660177242876280832_n.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQlfXbNVmycTVA5X43IW_qBDAFrQnI2BbDs4nNUnhd4da9IfUtZZWS3BMl1jhnlszNc&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=a7f9348492debb363fe116c2a5b6b622&amp;oe=5E0EC8BA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69168499_10157965156552448_4660177242876280832_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQlfXbNVmycTVA5X43IW_qBDAFrQnI2BbDs4nNUnhd4da9IfUtZZWS3BMl1jhnlszNc%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Da7f9348492debb363fe116c2a5b6b622%26oe%3D5E0EC8BA&h=5554bddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府就維園集會作出回應<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n政府發言人今日（八月十八日）回應在維多利亞公園舉辦的公眾集會時表示，雖然集會期間大致和平，但由於參與者佔用了港島多條主要幹道，路面交通大受影響，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>對市民造成不便</strong></span>。運輸署與警方已積極協調，盡量將影響減至最少。<br />\n<br />\n發言人重申，目前最重要的是要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>盡快回復社會秩序</strong></span>；<span style=\"color: red;\">當一切平靜之後</span>，政府會與市民展開真誠對話，致力修補撕裂，重建社會和諧。 <br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月18日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間22時18分<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請求立即針對政府聲明，開始諗要點樣升級</span>"},{"pid":"7bbf8119c5fdee245bb598abe4e9cd56e802609b","tid":1485691,"uid":30647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:38:44.000Z","msg":"agger 要諗下點善用 170萬 做文宣<br />\n香港 &amp; 外國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf121c1f89e0fd0cba64788dccb1365e1e44d94","tid":1485691,"uid":201385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6080936e3ee5f7352567b716d56dcab2d6236c","tid":1485691,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af961ce80a814be1336ca9ca641581431ef5c928","tid":1485691,"uid":201385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:29:28.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:39:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">【雨傘2.0】劉業成有心公開銅鑼灣班卧底 就係想大家一齊捉鬼</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1481711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1481711</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">認清楚係咪警察計謀 再決定點做<br />\n唔該手足</span>"},{"pid":"84961114fd1f1ce4e934aa171272a684137a4cb5","tid":1485691,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:41:20.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆 覺得今日仲多人過200萬個次"},{"pid":"ddd47c20cf162df6ee5e0dacbadada0a91d34126","tid":1485691,"uid":26672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:42:59.000Z","msg":"推，一定唔只1.7m，2500006人就差唔多"},{"pid":"fead3e677c945db705becdd12a9768cdd25f1f8f","tid":1485691,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:57:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce7e30930bb1b1ae44aa5bc3d7e2a0467fcaf972","tid":1485691,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/supp